			   cstermin History
			   ================

Version 0.03
   - Console Output is done now in UTF-8
   - Added Version parameter to command line
   - Appointments are now sorted by date for display
   - GTK2 Widget
     - Added separators between passed, today's and future appointments
     - Improved appointments alignment
     - Text Highlighting of "PASSED" and "TODAY" Appointments
     - Added Program Icon

Version 0.02
   - The character set of the config file is now UTF-8
   - Error messages are also displayed in a GTK widget, if available
   - It's now possible to copy text from the Gtk2 window


Version 0.01
   - Initial Release
